text: Accordion () is a 1934 Soviet movie directed by Igor Savchenko."Высокая награда" It stars Zoya Fyodorova, Pyotr Savin, and Igor Savchenko. ==Actors== * Zoya Fyodorova - Marusenka * Pyotr Savin - Timoshka * Igor Savchenko * Nikolay Gorlov - Mitya == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Russian comedy movies Category:1934 comedy movies Category:1934 musical movies Category:Movies directed by Igor Savchenko
title: Accordion (movie)
